{"tid":129074,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"Metal友入一入嚟","createTime":"2017-02-21T10:34:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-21T23:43:59.000Z","uid":82493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9d297a77f1b0e36bb87c68ab31fcc66ec1d46341","tid":129074,"uid":82493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T10:34:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/97ihwGhNZhY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F97ihwGhNZhY&d=Yo3BLZp%2B9L0ow7gqQKw5zQHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=0d95d7b3\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/97ihwGhNZhY</a><br />\n想問下13:40呢種core係邊種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搭單問多小小嘢，Metal core 有分幾多種<br />\n以我所認知得好小 就係scream分呼同吸<br />\n因為想學所以有無巴打可以推介一下點樣練到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3978bc030e9f4262d18a02c053145ed57b6238ae","tid":129074,"uid":82493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T10:43:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"585b05ce895d660695c79982af19e6436f039034","tid":129074,"uid":82493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T10:43:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11814c27dd4e3738ac77ef0efaab5e92b3993892","tid":129074,"uid":82493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T10:43:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f305f0784ebd9a248deeda0757ca4d3b98fd74bc","tid":129074,"uid":82493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T10:52:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"471b10ffdfeb82c3f85e7e4d130e6c5740b915f0","tid":129074,"uid":71140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T10:55:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0eab5e6223f350d752cdc7d0314170db8c90a1c1","tid":129074,"uid":82493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T11:02:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Core有分post hardcore, metalcore, deathcore <br />\n條片似post hardcore，即係冇咁重breakdown<br />\nMetalcore係其中一個genre, 主要既嗌有分高低兩種音</blockquote><br />\n巴打請問post hardcore 既發音位係邊到，同埋點樣練習<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0899503a7c65ab60c9b0e655910ffc89d2b9c25","tid":129074,"uid":71140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T11:14:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"780ef42fd8fd898eaf7a8f55a3d9299a9c5f00ae","tid":129074,"uid":23619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T11:22:05.000Z","msg":"上youtube既片夠你學識"},{"pid":"91218d016586b8ce3eadee404bec4a51c094cd9c","tid":129074,"uid":23619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T11:22:19.000Z","msg":"睇外國果啲人教"},{"pid":"2137c68af10980ceae177e7dfc1e9a1719abf564","tid":129074,"uid":82493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T11:29:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Core有分post hardcore, metalcore, deathcore <br />\n條片似post hardcore，即係冇咁重breakdown<br />\nMetalcore係其中一個genre, 主要既嗌有分高低兩種音</blockquote><br />\n巴打請問post hardcore 既發音位係邊到，同埋點樣練習<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n上網search有好多教學。應該都係要練丹田先，唔係既話好傷喉嚨<br />\n香港我知有隊叫門生既band，個主唱有開班教<br />\n利申番先 以上知識都係聽聽下累積番黎，非專業人士</blockquote><br />\nThank you你先巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c18c94ad7168e21d61491cf1703f8a027d777fae","tid":129074,"uid":38617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T11:31:29.000Z","msg":"Post hardcore 通常用hardcore scream<br />\n前提要掌握Fry scream先最好<br />\n<br />\n仲有個post名應該叫core仔入一入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66e1daebac101af9ec75c9f8ad3bba79f01777ed","tid":129074,"uid":82493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T11:59:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Post hardcore 通常用hardcore scream<br />\n前提要掌握Fry scream先最好<br />\n<br />\n仲有個post名應該叫core仔入一入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打可唔可以詳細講下Fry scream 係咩嚟，仲有個主題轉唔到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e52426773f915c9ee34cddaf6b4014fbbeef1791","tid":129074,"uid":37078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T12:43:16.000Z","msg":"Fry scream?"},{"pid":"1d981c9f7a528d0cd72f49646b243a432802a73c","tid":129074,"uid":23619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T23:43:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Post hardcore 通常用hardcore scream<br />\n前提要掌握Fry scream先最好<br />\n<br />\n仲有個post名應該叫core仔入一入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打可唔可以詳細講下Fry scream 係咩嚟，仲有個主題轉唔到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n學緊fry scream<br />\n照我自己理解，scream發聲方法有三大類，其他你聽到既就係由呢三種方法洐生出黎<br />\nFry, false chord, death <br />\n通常fry係高音啲，death最低音"}]}